0;"&gt;印度机构的模型预测表明，厄尔尼诺现象可能在印度降雨期间形成&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt;本周《零》 &lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div style="margin: 20px 0; background-color: #f5f5f5; border-radius: 12px; padding: 12px;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/HpFd_Zd84tMoJ4S0hc-h5vgoYL2EL4pHxkjBCkBv5t4tVmZVuhpou3I5BjgHbJe2MRGsR0rwxf04WwvOOwS6t1QooTvHm7vYVgOEviVDbNadiBIgcLusNKV3ZxjfHEl9XL9mNc5AeYyTeVdOvIyEtDjgDmRg7xctelLYBFBjz-ynkxKuAptxtlvSwA-_RGXptGuRqXfIkohgd8_WUlzbnPa9MdzeQqdcb1ZiUQkLgLdfhRYonkIkn52Z5zYemxZnQoKgPh6bbZsaELugnE4793oVuKjQqoqQ5SoCm6iXHt1vW36mAnTvH0d47EZ32luD3mO9kRrJS88EIAy57YGI_so01L2UYAy8fRc-xk5XMopwXEoJq7NdnpyT7cKui3Gp7I7Yn5rjtS4ZXeZ3FjAxQ_WbjG-VY2pla47mAkwIgt4xI0Muuc61Pk996dXQ0rs-PGMpIA7gGqQirJemhqKtKIf2M_W2MpWsa9GrxJa3QppLrE0wXi4EHFmP73sAAbff2ouKhCpf8awiwZQBeomyeUrtBGmOPoPLtJb9RCVAoBOuSg/ATzZadTNurhJyVSTmFbKfwAMJJOKPqwF/21" style="font-size: inherit; text-decoration: none; color: inherit;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse: collapse;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden;" valign="top" width="80"&gt;&lt;img alt="零" height="80" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iC1YpR5QCoRw/v13/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; border-radius: 10px;" width="80" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td width="12"&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td valign="top"&gt;&lt;p style="font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.4; margin: 0; color: inherit; font-size: 16px !important;"&gt;零&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="line-height: 1.2; margin: 4px 0 0 0; color: inherit; font-size: 16px !important;"&gt;各国正在谋划化石燃料时代的终结&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td width="12"&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td valign="bottom" width="28"&gt;&lt;img alt="立即收听" height="28" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ihClwsFiKu8o/v0/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; border-radius: 10px;" width="28" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&