rgin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;消息人士称，&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;欧盟正在考虑&lt;/strong&gt;暂时冻结对俄罗斯石油的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/KHkAPQQ3kIPylvyi2vXTAU_kE6MsET6AfCdGmIbXSLf_zm-Yqk9Gra0cJvlm8iTM0K9HqOwTAMGEtBa7E7a6lGhKVlD6cTejj0P1gDe7HFCFuq3CG-gE8km52L_mLw6g4k5oszNi2AJlA5_wsl6sS1LGeHIOgRjU1mr7RWinWiyrY2_rzMZdxYZfm_6Qgi7m63IeKqcr4Xowr41XXdHSQ9g-vNgXwCQKmef0ZF9A5VwgNaOfW8Bp0IHwXRgZiFxGKdJALasA_gZ78N4rGgf2brMujBSSoNTCUnelsPsMxVyFZOCN5nzutcDPZw6VJpGrYU66T7Aek2JPxAc70lXQFjhjIsBcOk-RpVFuIby3Qy8iDuBkBY4BrLp5994X7sgG2cqsRVt4cKf2oqAIeKcXAsBzziui1bSJxQfSGyykLd2sKjXne_8wnLYAi0ARqPZNyUEva1t4hSvpt5J3j_cs_95bcSOCnjGuqhZHMdXu1X1eEd3xm1RdXmRPlyukW7T1ue7q3XNamEIJGiSFlqN0BR2DzyqrlhGxWpvh2JPwXN3prg/HEztIF-p1kvTEl4jvg3Xt6GX2KXi3WB7/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="欧盟考虑暂时冻结俄罗斯石油价格上限以应对伊朗问题"&gt;价格上限&lt;/a&gt;。随着伊朗战争导致石油价格飙升，7 月份的下一次审查可能会看到价格上限水平至少升至 65 美元，高于七国集团此前设定的 60 美元门槛。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;克劳迪娅·希因鲍姆总统&lt;/strong&gt;对美国干预墨西哥国内政治的直率企图提出了&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/K9rMORFnUuk1JtBRChIBQ5jCN90x7nW4mjgoBmMBpAeYbNPcvqC6bmCz0xq06ND5SMDCZwpp2IYI0cNPNn_DcSnc-RnXQWIGr-3gc3HGNpnsa1QrK14h08wuiVFa9UkgI1zRME2MD70rG2ImqmyzPzfCm6Cd5o05n3E7G1Xr-3xv5EqDjUsb4MhBzvq8nQNwLpO3CGAPbaAivEBay1HfZwHbFf6VDrLe-tx1-nt5f-O12I3nJnY-iq7fyHk6zCcgZ8Hydcbf0eT1ODXglN6REdAXPuJ7WGneAARTvtAOYspS_j83eVYuC8nufB0JXeJWAOcSW-zuGbpMpW9SeIb8iT6ZWkQix7W9xn_oz_B24nhv2M_5eBF4Z1gELW6WN7MZS1CgS0eJ1khCGn3TwVhW5hOthrk5y5wBf04Qtdma2_wGN6mBboMA9HiAPi8qln01p0TNL6jeYG2Mw_8WvDt2h_vCbE3H8VbqtBpLMe7T1jEzerVhB0bMRhyX4XJAJoAUZPbGtPn4sXzI2Zs62Ta6pzlFut5wEsCi26zQ3A/QvACK-PxlafHisxrF6NoCOsyRiw8_JZY/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="希因鲍姆指责美国干涉墨西哥政治"&gt;迄今为止最强烈​​的批评&lt;/a&gt;。昨天，她在最近的演讲中反复出现的主题成为墨西哥城支持者的战斗口号，她声称，自 4 月 19 日两名中央情报局特工死亡以来，美国当局和极右翼团体加剧了破坏其政府稳定的行动。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-